-------------------------------------
FilePeruser Installation Instructions
-------------------------------------

1. Verify you meet the requirements in the README.
2. Follow these steps:
    a. cd to program directory (an open terminal here tool works, too)
    b. type "make"
    c. watch the compilation complete
    d. use the program
    Note: As of now, the program does not install to any directory.
        It simply compiles in the source directory.